; Program: Legal Compliance
; Objective: Assess if a contract draft complies with GDPR Article 6 standards.
; Output: Compliance result and identified non-compliant sections if applicable.

; Load the contract draft and the relevant GDPR article for analysis.
LF  X1, "examples/data/msa_draft_v2.txt"
LF  X2, "examples/data/gdpr_article_6.txt"

PSH X1              ; Push the contract draft onto the context stack for processing.
PSH X2              ; Push the GDPR article onto the context stack for reference.

; Does the contract draft comply with GDPR Article 6 standards?
LS  X3, "Does the contract draft comply with GDPR Article 6 standards above?"
AUD X4, X3          ; Audit the contract draft against GDPR Article 6.

LI  X3, 100         ; Audit will return 100 if the contract is fully compliant with GDPR Article 6.
BGE X4, X3, PASS

; Identify specific sections of the contract draft that do not comply with GDPR Article 6.
LS  X3, "Which specific sections of the contract are non-compliant with GDPR Article 6?"
COR X5, X2

LS  X3, "VIOLATIONS FOUND:"
OUT X3
OUT X5
EXIT

PASS:
LS  X3, "NO VIOLATIONS FOUND"
OUT X3
EXIT

